{"tid":1625483,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［和理非進場］入黎睇林鄭劇本","createTime":"2019-10-05T07:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T08:41:01.000Z","uid":157819,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1d3b82ab7f533ec614b8d1c242c24bca1ee2f5a2","tid":1625483,"uid":157819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:06:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TLDR：<br />\n國際線繼續做野，等sir this way，繼續twitter狂推緊急法<br />\n和理非全面進場，用人數對抗暴政，保護勇武<br />\n勇武適量行動，目標要明確</span></span><br />\n<br />\n條柒婆劇本好明顯，係要大家暴力升級，令國際同香港割蓆<br />\n咁急推蒙面推緊急法，預撚左你班勇武反彈預左比你尋晚出黎，所以尋晚係無警時分。<br />\n佢係怕左美國人權法案，想呢段時候暴力升級，令國際同香港割蓆，咁佢就大條道理止暴制亂，平亂有功。<br />\n<br />\n所以等緊sir this way既時候，和理非要全面進場！要用人數話比國際社會知香港人唔會放棄唔會怕惡法！勇武可以有適量行動但要目標明確，唔好招人口實！唔好急，記住呢場係長期戰！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n祈求民主與自由萬世都不朽<br />\n我願榮光歸香港</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"6245db904931e819f388ab1cdfb39994c4a99e66","tid":1625483,"uid":157819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:06:53.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"938f5f2636fee6c927d06b697859c8ed14ceee39","tid":1625483,"uid":157819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:07:54.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"f6a9e75ee67c3f1b30477544e8c7689a45920c24","tid":1625483,"uid":325706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:08:33.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"0396785ae8201fb51bd5619afb6e04ac8f3f7530","tid":1625483,"uid":157819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:20:04.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"a2c190c54d164a52029360df9ce708e6ffc5c439","tid":1625483,"uid":157819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:20:41.000Z","msg":"和理非進場"},{"pid":"794e5d734f84bde39b2f9e8c4af89b74cf4af30a","tid":1625483,"uid":157819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:22:39.000Z","msg":"勇武行